normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係要防既 係廚房門口掛串五帝錢 或者加個布廉<br />\n<br />\n最重要係 都唔係對正"},{"pid":"87c8f43cd64651e12784aa4551b7bc73d2372bf4","tid":2231473,"uid":342903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T00:26:44.000Z","msg":"你po floor plan 仲實際"},{"pid":"b7e924f07e6550fea82e4d7a9445ccb900799ef5","tid":2231473,"uid":87122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"長閂廚房門就做到屏風效果"},{"pid":"c48941b6c31d3320d425df64b10167a6c2a14b6e","tid":2231473,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"其實唔係對住灶頭就得㗎喇"},{"pid":"fcbbdddc9c643006aecb18fa5489274bf1fabbcf","tid":2231473,"uid":52669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"如果咁都係對 其實拉直線咩位都係對 <br />\n又唔係四合院 伯母偏on9 唔好曬錢啦"},{"pid":"1c18e616c46f33a3834953c45df88459ddd5356a","tid":2231473,"uid":52669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcbbdddc9c643006aecb18fa5489274bf1fabbcf","tid":2231473,"uid":52669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"如果咁都係對 其實拉直線咩位都係對 <br />\n又唔係四合院 伯母偏on9 唔好曬錢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"第日佢諗到有第樣野又心緒不靈 又要你改埋"},{"pid":"97547372d502a5f3129cd6f419f402d4627ac621","tid":2231473,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:47:57.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都對 你老母講曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf33f6b81b5eab39a157678b4b682dbd64125137","tid":2231473,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"952acc54161b133b2883cdc521860ff1173d2e56","tid":2231473,"uid":336509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"801f26b8769a3aea75bed78be5e45e298bc95b26","tid":2231473,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T16:23:29.000Z","msg":"可能我有少少腦退化啦<br />\n到底幅相大門喺邊 廚房門